id=update_blocker
name=Update Blocker
version=v1.0
versionCode=1
author=RAFSuNX
description=Fully blocks Android OTA updates at the root level: nulls out /system/bin/update_engine (the A/B payload applier) and disables the GMS/GSF/factoryota update-check services at boot. Use the KernelSU Manager "Action" button to reset update_engine status and clear cached OTA payloads on demand.
